g.text: Spas hot tub delivers the peace of mind that only
comes when you know that your investment is protected by the
most complete warranty in the hot tub industry.
How do we do it? Simple. If you make the best hot tub with
the most dependable, high-performance components, offering
the best warranty is just the logical next step. From precision
craftsmanship to rigorous quality control and testing, each Caldera
spa is scrutinized for form, function, fit and finish.
